Perhaps, the caterpillar from before was blocking my path to the hospital, as my route, [p]
which had been blocked until just before, was now restored.[p]
The entire town seemed like the insides of an enormous living thing.[p]
If a part of it is treated...then a part of it is destroyed.[p]
If a part of it disappears...then a part of it appears.[p]
I get the feeling that I am wandering about within a living organism that has become a labyrinth.[p]


